#. <section class="sutta" id="sn47.30"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn47.30:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 47"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 47"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn47.30:0.2"
msgid "3. Sīlaṭṭhitivagga"
msgstr "3. Ethics and Duration"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn47.30:0.3"
msgid "30. Mānadinnasutta"
msgstr "30. With Mānadinna"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli5.178"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.1"
msgid "Taṃyeva nidānaṃ."
msgstr "The same setting."

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena mānadinno gahapati ābādhiko hoti dukkhito bāḷhagilāno."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the householder Mānadinna was sick, suffering, gravely ill."

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho mānadinno gahapati aññataraṃ purisaṃ āmantesi:"
msgstr "Then he addressed a man:"

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.4"
msgid "“ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa … pe …"
msgstr "“Please, mister, go to Venerable Ānanda …” …"

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.5"
msgid ""
"na me, bhante, khamanīyaṃ na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā abhikkamanti, "
"no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamoti."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, I’m not keeping well, I’m not alright. The pain is terrible and "
"growing, not fading; its growing is evident, not its fading."

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.6"
msgid ""
"Evarūpāya cāhaṃ, bhante, dukkhāya vedanāya phuṭṭho samāno kāye kāyānupassī "
"viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke abhijjhādomanassaṃ;"
msgstr ""
"When I experience such painful feelings I meditate observing an aspect of "
"the body—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the world."

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.7"
msgid "vedanāsu … pe …"
msgstr "I meditate observing an aspect of feelings …"

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.8"
msgid "citte … pe …"
msgstr "mind …"

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.9"
msgid ""
"dhammesu dhammānupassī viharāmi ātāpī sampajāno satimā, vineyya loke "
"abhijjhādomanassaṃ."
msgstr ""
"principles—keen, aware, and mindful, rid of desire and aversion for the "
"world."

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.10"
msgid ""
"Yāni cimāni, bhante, bhagavatā pañcorambhāgiyāni saṃyojanāni desitāni, "
"nāhaṃ, bhante, tesaṃ kiñci attani appahīnaṃ samanupassāmī”ti."
msgstr ""
"And of the five lower fetters taught by the Buddha, I don’t see any that I "
"haven’t given up.”"

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.11"
msgid "“Lābhā te, gahapati, suladdhaṃ te, gahapati."
msgstr "“You’re fortunate, householder, so very fortunate!"

msgctxt "sn47.30:1.12"
msgid "Anāgāmiphalaṃ tayā, gahapati, byākatan”ti."
msgstr "You have declared the fruit of non-return.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.13"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn47.30:1.14"
msgid "Sīlaṭṭhitivaggo tatiyo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.1"
msgid "Sīlaṃ ṭhiti parihānaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.2"
msgid "suddhaṃ brāhmaṇapadesaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.3"
msgid "Samattaṃ loko sirivaḍḍho,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn47.30:2.4"
msgid "mānadinnena te dasāti."
msgstr ""
